            <title>[MRUNIT-8] Fix failing testConfiguration tests</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MRUNIT-8</link>
                <project id="12311292" key="MRUNIT">MRUnit</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The testConfiguration() tests from TestMapDriver, TestReduceDriver, and TestMapReduceDriver are failing. Not sure if I screwed up &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MRUNIT-6&quot; title=&quot;Reverse MAPREDUCE-954 in trunk&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;MRUNIT-6&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;MRUNIT-6&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; or if these always failed. They should be fixed (or removed if they don&apos;t test something meaningful).&lt;/p&gt;</description>
